<entry id="determinación" guid="cd610758-f3bd-5e43-b00a-7f4badcfce6b"><lexical-unit><form lang="es"><text>determinación</text></form></lexical-unit><trait name="morph-type" value="stem"/><sense id="determinación_0" guid="2be779f7-fed1-5091-bee9-1424e4d9838b"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>determination, identification, establishment, establishing (i.e. figuring out something with relative certainty)</text></gloss></sense><sense id="determinación_1" guid="16b3214d-da25-53bb-bf2c-66e7b23faf77"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>determination, resolve, resoluteness (i.e. firmness of purpose or intention)</text></gloss></sense><sense id="determinación_2" guid="180a20b3-31aa-54f9-afda-4d92707ad1f1"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>decision</text></gloss></sense><sense id="determinación_3" guid="f58b1789-deed-5a14-b519-930541e3dc2a"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>setting, fixing, determining (e.g. fixing of a deadline, setting of objectives or goals)</text></gloss></sense><sense id="determinación_4" guid="76380391-06d9-59cb-a14e-a3324c8c3b2e"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>firmness</text></gloss></sense></entry>
