<entry id="nacer" guid="7cb7b60a-3ef2-50d9-901d-bba53708505b"><lexical-unit><form lang="es"><text>nacer</text></form></lexical-unit><trait name="morph-type" value="stem"/><sense id="nacer_0" guid="c555d2d5-7085-5956-aad5-b68e97aac7c3"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to be born, to sprout, to begin to grow; to hatch (out)</text></gloss></sense><sense id="nacer_1" guid="62a2cd04-6c64-59dc-afa1-8ad3334cf86a"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to grow; to rise, to have its source (river); to rise (sun); to have its roots; to arise</text></gloss></sense></entry>
