<entry id="roma" guid="3ac4c0e9-5207-5ec7-8cfb-f1bb53ea49a1"><lexical-unit><form lang="es"><text>roma</text></form></lexical-unit><trait name="morph-type" value="stem"/><sense id="roma_0" guid="395ea582-a4e9-59a9-8c19-14dcbbecc6cb"><grammatical-info value="Proper noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>Rome (a major city, the capital of Italy and the Italian region of Lazio, located on the Tiber River; the ancient capital of the Roman Empire)</text></gloss></sense><sense id="roma_1" guid="933392e0-6c28-5174-b129-2b82e0fe0d54"><grammatical-info value="Proper noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>Rome (a metropolitan city of Lazio, Italy)</text></gloss></sense><sense id="roma_2" guid="4d60d358-a912-58b0-a583-6a47a053ee65"><grammatical-info value="Proper noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>Rome, Ancient Rome (an ancient empire based out of the city of Rome, covering vast territories in Europe, Asia and Africa; in full, Roman Empire)</text></gloss></sense></entry>
