<entry id="tapar" guid="ac5c181d-32b6-563f-bf07-0d4d76a61952"><lexical-unit><form lang="es"><text>tapar</text></form></lexical-unit><trait name="morph-type" value="stem"/><sense id="tapar_0" guid="cfde4bed-736f-53c0-94ed-f4f652238a84"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to cover</text></gloss></sense><sense id="tapar_1" guid="482b2875-65f2-5b94-8cd7-ea2a64c88fb0"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to cap, to close with a lid, to put a lid on</text></gloss></sense><sense id="tapar_2" guid="2b874846-c66b-5363-bb03-f540fc644148"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to plug, to plug up, to fill a hole or pit</text></gloss></sense><sense id="tapar_3" guid="f704b9d9-d580-5491-be63-cf0f8d5c4d25"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to block, to obstruct, to clog</text></gloss></sense><sense id="tapar_4" guid="d51005f5-5bd4-5f99-919d-ffee8db0693d"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to cover up, to hide, to conceal</text></gloss></sense><sense id="tapar_5" guid="5d4cc067-1b36-5233-af5c-9b305513e58e"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to mask (e.g., a smell, a painting or colors painted)</text></gloss></sense><sense id="tapar_6" guid="5335f12e-c836-5c04-97c2-653e7b99b960"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to be clogged, to be clogged up</text></gloss></sense><sense id="tapar_7" guid="c8418a84-a50d-542e-aede-bce5cf730898"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to cover oneself up (to cover oneself when naked)</text></gloss></sense></entry>
